                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                {{/if}}
                                
                                <!-- Primary CTA -->
                                <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 32px 0;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td align="center">
                                            <a href="{{dashboard_url}}" class="btn">
                                                🚀 Access Your Dashboard
                                            </a>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                                
                                <!-- Premium Features -->
                                <div class="content-section">
                                    <h2>✨ Your Premium Features</h2>
                                    <p>With your active subscription, you have full access to:</p>
                                    
                                    <div class="feature-list">
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">📝</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>AI-Powered Journaling</strong> - Get sentiment analysis and business insights</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">🎯</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>Advanced Goal Tracking</strong> - Milestone-based progress with visual indicators</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">📊</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>BizBuilder Tools</strong> - Financial calculators and business planning tools</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">🎓</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>Podcast Training</strong> - Exclusive entrepreneurial content and courses</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">📁</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>Secure Document Management</strong> - Store and organize your business files</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-item">
                                            <span class="feature-icon">📧</span>
                                            <span class="feature-text"><strong>Personalized Daily Emails</strong> - Custom business insights delivered daily</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- What's Next -->
                                <div class="content-section">
                                    <h2>🚀 What's next?</h2>
                                    <p><strong>Ready to grow your business?</strong> Here are some recommended next steps:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>📈 Set up your business goals and milestones in the Goals section</li>
                                        <li>💡 Start journaling to track your entrepreneurial journey</li>
