                                        <li>🎥 Check out the latest podcast episodes for business insights</li>
                                        <li>📊 Review your personalized dashboard for business metrics</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- Support -->
                                <div class="content-section">
                                    <h2>💬 Need help?</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        Our support team is here to help you succeed! If you have any questions about your subscription or need assistance,
                                        <a href="mailto:support@bizzin.co.za" style="color: #EA7A57;">contact support</a> and we'll get back to you quickly.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- Footer Message -->
                                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 32px 0 0 0; padding: 24px 0 0 0; text-align: center;">
                                    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        Thank you for choosing Bizzin to power your entrepreneurial journey. We're excited to help you achieve your business goals!
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    
                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <div class="footer">
                        <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="content-block">
                                    <span>Bizzin - Empowering Entrepreneurs</span><br>
                                    <span>This is a payment confirmation for your subscription.</span><br>
                                    <a href="{{unsubscribe_url}}">Unsubscribe from payment notifications</a>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
